    <h4 class="text-info">Agriculture</h4>
    <p>
        Eight Out Of 10 People Are Engaged In Farming .Rolling Fields And Neat Terraces Can Be Seen All Over The Hills Of Sikkim. Even In The Highly Urbanized Gangtok, Large Tracts Of Land Outside The Areas Are Devoted To Farming. Rice Is The Staple Diet In Sikkim. Other Major Crops Are Maize, Wheat, Millet And Barley. Besides Food Grains, Cash Crops Like Cardamom, Ginger, Orange And Tea Are Also Cultivated In Some Areas Of State.
